PN,39601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FA man who "did not seem bothered",
OL,8,Fafter he stabbed his ex-wife to death
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for life, and will
OL,10,Fserve at least 14 years.
OL,12,FGavin Shaw, 62, admitted to stabbing
OL,13,Fhis ex-partner, Michele Kennedy,
OL,14,Finside their former home in Warrington
OL,15,Fin October 2025.
OL,17,FThe 55-year-old victim was said to
OL,18,Fhave been on the cusp of a "new lease
OL,19,Fof life" following the end of their
OL,20,F"volatile and toxic" relationship,
OL,21,FLiverpool Crown Court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FThey split around three months before
OL,8,Fthe attack, having been married for 12
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FAndrew Ford KC, prosecuting, said
OL,12,Fpeople who had known the couple knew
OL,13,Fthey were having "problems" and Shaw
OL,14,Fwould often go and stay with his son,
OL,15,FAdam, when he and Michele had domestic
OL,16,Fdifficulties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FHe said: "Mr Shaw's son described a
OL,8,Fvolatile relationship between his
OL,9,Ffather and the deceased and he said,
OL,10,Fas well as his father's alcoholism, Ms
OL,11,FKennedy herself could contribute
OL,12,Ftowards the friction that lay between
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Michele's mother Patricia said that
OL,16,Falcohol was, as she put it, a
OL,17,Fpermanent issue in the relationship
OL,18,Fbetween her daughter and Gavin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"She said and recognises that, whilst
OL,8,Fher daughter could be stubborn and
OL,9,Fargumentative, the root cause of the
OL,10,Fproblem was the defendant's drinking. "
OL,12,FHe told the court that there were
OL,13,Ftimes in their relationship where the
OL,14,Fpolice were called.
OL,16,FMichele's mum Patricia Lawton
OL,17,Fdescribed her daughter as "feeling
OL,18,Fdifferently about life, being in a
OL,19,Fbetter place, looking after her
OL,20,Fappearance and moving on" since their
OL,21,Fsplit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FWhile they were on holiday between 19-
OL,8,F26 September 2025, she had "had a
OL,9,Fromance" with a man she had met
OL,10,Fabroad, Gordon Riddick. But the court
OL,11,Fheard that Shaw continued to "pester"
OL,12,Fhis ex via text messages while she was
OL,13,Faway.
OL,15,FMr Ford continued: "It is important
OL,16,Fthat the court understands that those
OL,17,Fwho knew her well speak variously of
OL,18,Fher having a fresh outlook and a new
OL,19,Flease of life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"Mr Shaw's murder of her was not the
OL,8,Fact of a man scorned by infidelity.
OL,9,FThis relationship was over. She had
OL,10,Fbegun a new chapter in her life.
OL,12,F"Other relationships she had, for
OL,13,Fexample, that with her mother, were
OL,14,Fundoubtedly improving. She was making
OL,15,Fdecisions of her own, one of them to
OL,16,Fgo on holiday with her mother to
OL,17,FTurkey. She did that just before she
OL,18,Fwas killed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FMr Ford said: "Mr Riddick described
OL,8,Fhow he developed strong feelings for
OL,9,FMichele Kennedy quite quickly. He said
OL,10,Fthat they were inseparable for the
OL,11,Fsecond part of the holiday. He said
OL,12,Fthat she feared Gavin's reaction if he
OL,13,Ffound out that she had met somebody
OL,14,Felse."
OL,16,FHe told the court the couple spent the
OL,17,Fweekend before her murder together in
OL,18,FLiverpool and Southport, separating on
OL,19,FSunday 12 October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FHe said: "On Monday the 13th, Mr
OL,8,FRiddick's affectionate WhatsApp
OL,9,Fmessaging with Michele began to go
OL,10,Funanswered mid-afternoon. He began to
OL,11,Fworry.
OL,13,F"Later on Monday, a friend of
OL,14,FMichele's texted him to say that she
OL,15,Fhad been stabbed and was seriously ill
OL,16,Fin hospital. The weekend, after he was
OL,17,Finformed that she had died."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FThe day before the murder, Shaw was
OL,8,Fsaid to have messaged Ms Kennedy's
OL,9,Fmum, son and a "mutual contact" saying
OL,10,F"never thought she was a slag",
OL,11,Faccompanied by "vomiting emojis",
OL,12,Fafter he had "plainly got wind of the
OL,13,Ffact that Michele had been with a man".
OL,15,FMr Ford said that on the 13 October:
OL,16,F"After work, in the early afternoon,
OL,17,Fthe defendant and his son went for a
OL,18,Fdrink at the local Warrington
OL,19,FConservative Club. Footage showed that
OL,20,Fthe dad and son drank several pints.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"A witness noted that Gavin 'appeared
OL,8,Flike he was just having a pint after
OL,9,Fwork, as I've seen him do many times'.
OL,10,F'He didn't seem agitated. When he
OL,11,Fleft, he appeared his normal self,
OL,12,Fsaying goodbye to me'."
OL,14,FShaw was seen on Ring doorbell camera
OL,15,Ffootage approaching Ms Kennedy's home,
OL,16,Fbeing "noted to discernibly pause and
OL,17,Ftake a moment" before turning the
OL,18,Fhandle of the front door and entering.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FMr Ford added: "The defendant emerged,
OL,8,Fto the second, three minutes later
OL,9,Fexactly. It is the prosecution's case
OL,10,Fthat, while inside for those three
OL,11,Fminutes, Gavin Shaw murdered Michele
OL,12,FKennedy by stabbing her in the chest
OL,13,Ftwice with a kitchen knife."
OL,15,F"There is limited evidence of what
OL,16,Fhappened at the scene. Her handset was
OL,17,Ffound submerged in water in the
OL,18,Fkitchen sink. The defendant had not
OL,19,Fvisited pre-armed with the knife, not
OL,20,Fwith any weapon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"Once inside the address, he took up
OL,8,Fthe knife from a set of knives which
OL,9,Fshe kept in the kitchen. They were
OL,10,Fbought for her as a gift from her
OL,11,Fmother.
OL,13,F"The footage captures Michele Kennedy
OL,14,Femerge first. She is followed
OL,15,Fimmediately by the defendant, but they
OL,16,Fare separate. There is no struggle nor
OL,17,Fcommotion. It is just three minutes
OL,18,Fafter his entry. She got to the end of
OL,19,Fher garden path, turned right down
OL,20,FManchester Road and slumped to the
OL,21,Fpavement."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FShaw was seen "milling about on the
OL,8,Fpavement" beside the busy main road
OL,9,Fwhile numerous vehicles passed the
OL,10,Fscene. One member of the public
OL,11,Frecalled seeing him "standing calmly
OL,12,Fover her, looking down", with a
OL,13,Fpicture which was taken by one witness
OL,14,Fhaving shown Ms Kennedy by now in
OL,15,Fpossession of the knife with a
OL,16,F"distressed" look on her face.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FTwo passing workmen then approached,
OL,8,Fwith one kicking the weapon away
OL,9,Fbetween two wheelie bins. One of them,
OL,10,FLouie Holt, called 999 after finding
OL,11,FMichele "gasping and asking for her
OL,12,Finhaler".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FShaw was described as "acting calmly,
OL,8,Fwithout emotion", with Mr Ford saying:
OL,9,F"He offered a slight smile to Mr Holt.
OL,10,FThe defendant lit a cigarette. The
OL,11,Fwitness formed the impression that the
OL,12,Fdefendant, quote, did not seem
OL,13,Fbothered. The witness, said that he
OL,14,Fwas scared by the extent of the
OL,15,Fdefendant's despondency."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FAdam Shaw was also home at the time
OL,8,Fand "heard Mr Shaw confess", saying
OL,9,Fthat he had "used a Ninja knife to
OL,10,Fstab Michele". Adam then grabbed hold
OL,11,Fof a towel and rushed to Ms Kennedy's
OL,12,Faid while his father "went and sat in
OL,13,Fthe back garden and had a cigarette".
OL,15,FMr Ford said another witness, Hailey
OL,16,FHiggins, heard Shaw shouting "she's a
OL,17,Fslag". He said Hayley knelt down on
OL,18,Fthe pavement and gave Michele an
OL,19,Finhaler, who said "he stabbed me".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"Emergency personnel attended, and
OL,8,Fsignificant attempts were made to save
OL,9,FMichele Kennedy's life. Her condition
OL,10,Fwas deteriorating. The knife had
OL,11,Fcaused substantial damage to a number
OL,12,Fof her internal organs, and a
OL,13,Fconsultant surgeon was flown to the
OL,14,Fscene."
OL,16,FHaving suffered stab wounds to her
OL,17,Fstomach and liver, with the blood
OL,18,Fsupply to several other organs also
OL,19,Fbeing cut off, Ms Kennedy underwent
OL,20,Fseveral rounds of surgery, but died as
OL,21,Fa result of her injuries on 18 October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FShaw was estimated to be twice the
OL,8,Fdrink driving limit at the time of the
OL,9,Fincident, saying in a prepared
OL,10,Fstatement under interview following
OL,11,Fhis arrest: "I want to say that I'm
OL,12,Fdevastated at what has happened. I
OL,13,Fdidn't intend to kill Michele.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"Everything happened very quickly. I
OL,8,Ffelt emotionally overwhelmed and in
OL,9,Fshock. I didn't make any conscious
OL,10,Fdecision. It was a reaction in the
OL,11,Fheat of the moment. It felt like I
OL,12,Fsnapped. I just grabbed the kitchen
OL,13,Fknife from the side in the kitchen.
OL,14,FI'm in complete shock."
OL,16,FShaw was informed of Michele's death
OL,17,Fwhile in custody at HMP Altcourse on
OL,18,F19 October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39620
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FMembers of prison staff said in their
OL,8,Fevidence that he was "tearful and
OL,9,F"distressed" at the news and
OL,10,Fcommented: "It should never have got
OL,11,Fthat far. I'd been screaming at her
OL,12,Fbecause she'd been on her back getting
OL,13,Fs***ged in Manchester."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39621
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775304668
OL,3,CMan who 'did not seem bothered' after
OL,4,Cfatally stabbing ex-wife jailed for
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FA mental health nurse meanwhile
OL,8,Freported hearing Shaw saying "f***, I
OL,9,Fshouldn't have done it" after being
OL,10,Ftold Michele had died. He also stated
OL,11,Fthat he and Ms Kennedy had "argued
OL,12,Fabout the weekend" and that she had
OL,13,F"denied sleeping with the other man"
OL,14,Fbefore he had stabbed her.
OL,16,FShaw pleaded guilty to murder at a
OL,17,Fhearing in February 2026.
OL,19,FHe has been sentenced to life in jail,
OL,20,Fto serve a minimum of 14 years.
